            <p><strong>Geometry Dash Lite</strong> is the free version of the popular Geometry Dash game. It features a curated selection of levels perfect for players who want to experience the core gameplay without purchasing the full version. The lite version maintains all the exciting mechanics and challenging gameplay that made Geometry Dash famous, making it ideal for beginners and casual players.</p>
          </div>
          
